<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <title>Vuerails</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
    integrity="sha384-Zenh87qX5JnK2Jl0vWa8Ck2rdkQ2Bzep5IDxbcnCeuOxjzrPF/et3URy9Bv1WTRi" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
    integrity="sha384-OERcA2EqjJCMA+/3y+gxIOqMEjwtxJY7qPCqsdltbNJuaOe923+mo//f6V8Qbsw3"
    crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  <style type="text/css">
  </style>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
    <%= csp_meta_tag %>
      <%= stylesheet_link_tag "application" %>
        <%= vite_client_tag %>
          <%= vite_javascript_tag 'application' %>
            <!--
      If using a TypeScript entrypoint file:
        vite_typescript_tag 'application'

      If using a .jsx or .tsx entrypoint, add the extension:
        vite_javascript_tag 'application.jsx'

      Visit the guide for more information: https://vite-ruby.netlify.app/guide/rails
    -->

            <%= vite_client_tag %>
              <%= vite_javascript_tag 'application' %>
                <!--
      If using a TypeScript entrypoint file:
        vite_typescript_tag 'application'

      If using a .jsx or .tsx entrypoint, add the extension:
        vite_javascript_tag 'application.jsx'

      Visit the guide for more information: https://vite-ruby.netlify.app/guide/rails
    -->

</head>

<body>
  <%= render 'welcome/header' %>
    <div class="container-fluid">
      <div id="carouselExampleCaptions" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
        <div class="carousel-indicators">
          <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active"
            aria-current="true" aria-label="Slide 1"></button>
          <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="1"
            aria-label="Slide 2"></button>
          <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="2"
            aria-label="Slide 3"></button>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-inner">
          <div class="carousel-item active" data-bs-interval="6000">
            <%= image_tag "peakpx.jpg" , id:"first-image", class:"w-100" %>
              <h1 id="first-text-title" class="content-title">Encontre sua academia ideal.</h1>
              <h1 id="first-text-content" class="content">
                Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.
                Fusce ornare risus purus, eu dictum tellus volutpat nec.
                Cras sed enim erat. Maecenas at nisl tellus. Vestibulum ante ipsum primis in faucibus orci luctus et
                ultrices posuere cubilia curae;
                Aliquam erat volutpat. Nullam sit amet rhoncus nunc. Duis ac odio ultrices, feugiat ligula ac, dapibus
                leo.
              </h1>
              <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary mt-5">Saiba mais</button>
              <div class="carousel-caption d-none">
              </div>
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item" data-bs-interval="6000">
            <%= image_tag "second_image.jpg" , id:"second-image", class:"w-100" %>
              <h1 id="second-text-title" class="content-title">De sua casa até seu trabalho.</h1>
              <%= image_tag "maps_placeholder.jpg" , id:"placeholder-maps"%>
                <h1 id="second-text-content" class="content">
                  Com nosso recurso de geolocalização, é possível que você, a partir de um dado endereço,
                  encontre e descubra as academias e centros esportivos mais próximos!
                </h1>
                <button id="map-button" type="button" class="btn btn-primary">Teste já</button>
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none">
                </div>
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item" data-bs-interval="6000">
            <%= image_tag "third_image.jpg" , id:"third-image", class:"w-100" %>
              <h1 id="third-text-title" class="content-title">Isso e muito mais em um só lugar.</h1>
              <h1 id="third-text-content1" class="content">
                Com a WeGoGym, você pode encontrar sua academia ideal com poucos cliques.
                Além da funcionalidade de geolocalização, você terá acesso às diversas informações
                que uma academia de seu interesse possui, como mensalidade, avaliações e muito mais!
              </h1>
              <h1 id="third-text-content2" class="content">
                Faça parte da família WeGoGym!
              </h1>
              <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary mt-5">Cadastre-se</button>
              <div class="carousel-caption d-none">
              </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions"
          data-bs-slide="prev">
          <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
        </button>
        <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions"
          data-bs-slide="next">
          <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <%= yield %>
      <footer id="footer-main-page">
        <h1 id="footer-main-page-content">Footer protótipo</h1>
        <h2 id="footer-main-page-mark">WeGoGym&copy;</h2>
      </footer>

      <div id="app">
        <p>{{ course }}</p>
        <button-counter></button-counter>
      </div>
</body>

</html>